Share information
Cube Storage Pioneers

Little Robots, Big Business

Since its inception in 1996, AutoStore™ has worked to improve warehouse efficiency. Today, the company’s key value proposition is to deliver an easy-to-use software powered cubic automatic storage and retrieval ecosystem.

The AutoStore solution is modular and flexible, and can automate any warehouse. The system offers a superior customer value proposition across operating metrics, ESG scores, and customer economics.
‍

View video to learn more

entry.title: Cyprian Norwid (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that the 19th-century poet Cyprian Norwid (pictured), now recognized as one of the most important Polish poets, led a poverty-stricken life and his works were rarely appreciated until decades after his death?

entry.content: ... that ancient Rome's Temple of Piety was closely connected with the legend of a daughter who breastfed an imprisoned parent?

entry.content: ... that the librarian Paul Needham has argued for the "respectful burial of the human remains" included in a book bound in human skin?
